cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image descriptors and pedestrian detection. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes a discriminative model. Multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) are less likely but still possible sub-categories as the paper mentions datasets and discrimination performance.
